Commentary Text: Sandeep Sharma to de Kock, out Bowled!! Full and wide, a full-toss in fact, and the lack of pace has done him in! Commentary Text: Sandeep Sharma to Rohit, out Caught by Warner! Immature shot by Sharma! A player of his caliber should know better than to trust the bounce and pace of a pitch this early. Benefit of the doubt to him, perhaps, because it's his first innings back. This was swerving away a little bit from a good length, a knuckle ball in fact to take the pace off, and Rohit tried to loft this over mid-off, lazily as he does all the time, but doesn't get the timing or the elevation as Warner dives forward to complete a catch. A truncated stay out in the middle for Rohit. Rohit c Warner b Sandeep Sharma 4(7)
